{"tid":1242543,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[信不信由你]烈士只想帶5個字比大家","createTime":"2019-06-19T05:47:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T05:48:04.000Z","uid":67115,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e4687576ae9a205a6978b49f7ecd0b4e0f3824d1","tid":1242543,"uid":67115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:47:13.000Z","msg":"是咁的 小妹拜開觀音 <br />\n自細有靈異體質但無開天眼 有修行<br />\n16號朝早去左PP放低兩份手抄經文就去左返工<br />\n16號晚放工遊行完返到屋企3點幾一個人訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係床到唔想合埋眼一直追現場新聞<br />\n突然耳邊傳來男聲深嘆「唉」<br />\n<br />\n今日早上諗諗下去搵法科朋友傾計<br />\n未同師父講咩事 師父已經見到我身後有位男性靈體<br />\n經過一番對話後<br />\n原來係16號早上唔小心撞到烈士令佢跟住左我幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正常自殺既靈魂係要先去地獄審判受罪先再輪迴<br />\n觀音娘娘開恩 會送烈士上天堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n烈士離開前留低左五個字<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人加油</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我喊到完全收唔到聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />師傅都眼濕濕<br />\n出呢個Post唔係炒作 預左比唔信既人怒屌<br />\n但香港人要加油 團結一致 各自爬山<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我地一定會贏！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"94e11e8c063e32f1424afdbd034e62bf9c8583f4","tid":1242543,"uid":249971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T05:48:04.000Z","msg":"10\\10"}]}